        {
            "title": "伊朗不是委內瑞拉 特朗普「戰略誤判」正在付出代價",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"伊朗不是委內瑞拉 特朗普「戰略誤判」正在付出代價\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cQAdiumRF7NBOy7Y4Q4qJQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/8b4b9c10-1e93-11f1-9f77-cff67d17f3e4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">伊朗不是委內瑞拉 特朗普「戰略誤判」正在付出代價</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
