            "title": "中國｜阿里雲手機龍蝦App上線",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"中國｜阿里雲手機龍蝦App上線\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國｜阿里雲手機龍蝦App上線</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿里巴巴(09988)旗下阿里雲手機版OpenClaw(「龍蝦」)—JVS Claw已上線App Store等應用商店，用戶也可以通過阿里雲網站訪問。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">官方指，JVS Claw是一款集成AI智能助手(Clawbot)與雲端獨立環境(ClawSpace)的創新產品。JVS Claw的核心目標在於「執行」，用戶可通過簡單的自然語言指令，驅動Clawbot在ClawSpace雲端環境中操作應用、處理文件、完成複雜的任務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">JVS Claw內測期間，每位用戶可免費創建1個bot，每人默認提供8000Credits免費額度，有效期14天。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E9%9B%B2%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%BE%8D%E8%9D%A6app%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A-040926187.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 12:13:08",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "短炒波士｜避險情緒仍高漲 宜看短線及縮注碼｜Ringo",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"350\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ChLEThLWPH5WQEgTs86I.Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bossmind_356/ebfa43845a5162128fbbc8a579c1abcd\" width=\"620\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊衝突未見有緩和跡象，市場避險情緖依然高漲，預期港股近日的反彈已經完成，暫時會在本月分水嶺26,500點以下游走。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">地緣政治風險難測，港股波動性明顯增加，投資者應以短線方式應對，並要縮細注碼。若恒指跌至25,000點附近可考慮搏反彈，升至26,200點至26,400點則可考慮做淡，但應採用牛熊證或買入認購期權（Long Call）或認沽期權（Long Put）作為工具，避免承受難以計算的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股方面，標普500指數短線技術走勢欠佳，料會大致橫行向下，支持位料在6,500點。投資者可靜候低吸，作中長線部署。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-559861b4-a949-3d00-8457-e0a5cb88fec8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，台積電（TSM）及TESLA（TSLA）可睇位低吸，前者跌至320美元或以下時可開始買入，後者380美元及390美元短炒，反彈至410美元至420美元便食糊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Ringo<br/>資深投資者<br/>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://signup.hkiei.com/ringo_webinar_bossmind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/f5ebMigAFcz9pgYh2d2zRA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bossmind_356/f52012128630469615370091d56ff897\" width=\"960\"/></div></a></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9F%AD%E7%82%92%E6%B3%A2%E5%A3%AB-%E9%81%BF%E9%9A%AA%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E4%BB%8D%E9%AB%98%E6%BC%B2-%E5%AE%9C%E7%9C%8B%E7%9F%AD%E7%B7%9A%E5%8F%8A%E7%B8%AE%E6%B3%A8%E7%A2%BC-ringo-041500288.html",
